  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>%%This item is used by the Jez's Wall of Fire Macro don't casually mess with it, please%%</strong></p>\n<p>When a target should be subject to Wall of Fire from <strong>%ATOKEN%</strong>'s wall of fire, target the token to be damaged and manually use this spell to inflict&nbsp;<strong>%NUMDICE%d8</strong> fire damage, subject to a saving throw.</p>\n<p>When the wall appears, each creature within the wall is immdiately subject to damage.</p>\n<p>One side of the wall, selected by you when you cast this spell, deals damage to each creature that ends its turn within 10 feet of that side or inside the wall. A creature takes the same damage when it enters or pass through the wall for the first time on a turn or ends its turn there. The other side of the wall deals no damage.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>FoundryVTT</strong>: This spell is to be used manually to inflict damage when appropriate.</p>",
